{"type":"message","id":"2234d0d8","parentId":"7ac3e26b","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:10:28.289Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我是否还记得他是谁，以及他最近准备干什么事。根据 AGENTS.md 的指引，我应该：\n\n1. 读取 SOUL.md（已加载）- 了解我是谁\n2. 读取 USER.md（已加载）- 了解用户是谁\n3. 读取 memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md（今天 + 昨天）- 获取最近上下文\n4. 如果在 MAIN SESSION（直接聊天）：还要读取 MEMORY.md\n\n当前日期是 2026-03-29，所以我需要读取：\n- memory/2026-03-29.md（今天）\n- memory/2026-03-28.md（昨天）\n- MEMORY.md（长期记忆）\n\n让我先读取这些文件来了解用户的近况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我先回顾一下记忆文件，看看最近发生了什么。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_48ae6030f105485192a933c5","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot\\MEMORY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_33a917f403344f79a473478f","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot\\memory\\2026-03-29.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f3904b593bc9451fb2af6e9b","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot\\memory\\2026-03-28.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":18827,"output":402,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19229,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774746586263,"responseId":"b45338f22a3fee4892a502c5808ed43a"}}
