{"type":"message","id":"ada7add8","parentId":"7e52bf9d","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:10:40.544Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来记忆文件还不存在，这是一个新的会话。让我根据已加载的 USER.md 来回答用户的问题。\n\n根据 USER.md：\n- **Name:** 长安爸爸\n- **What to call them:** 主人\n- **职业:** 芯片验证工程师\n- **目前项目:** 主攻 WiFi 6/7 PHY 物理层验证，每一代包含 AP 和 STA 两个模块，后续会持续推进 WiFi 8 相关验证项目\n- **Notes:** 喜欢技术类的东西，近期计划系统学习 WiFi PHY 物理层\n\n所以用户是长安爸爸，他最近准备系统学习 WiFi PHY 物理层。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"当然记得！主人～ 🤖\n\n你是**长安爸爸**，芯片验证工程师，专注于 **WiFi 6/7 PHY 物理层验证**，每一代项目包含 AP 和 STA 两个模块。\n\n**最近准备做的事：**\n- 📚 **系统学习 WiFi PHY 物理层** — 这是你在 USER.md 里记录的近期计划\n- 后续还会持续推进 **WiFi 8** 相关验证项目\n\n这些都是从你的 `USER.md` 里读到的。不过记忆目录（memory/）目前还是空的，所以我们之前的对话细节我暂时没存下来。\n\n有什么具体想规划或推进的吗？比如学习计划、项目进度、或者想让我帮你记录点什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":19255,"output":419,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19674,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774746628334,"responseId":"4b4fa77f461b2fc9148f7a6009081c01"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b7d88542","parentId":"ada7add8","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:12:31.949Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53b3891bdca4b36a8906f68336f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 09:12 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b53b3891bdca4b36a8906f68336f]\nou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf: 帮我规划一份wifi phy学习计划，按照先时域后频域的流程，每天学习一个小时，难度适合我的角色，学习内容写入到飞书分档中，然后发给我"}],"timestamp":1774746751947}}
{"type":"message","id":"0ef5904d","parentId":"b7d88542","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:12:41.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要：\n1. 规划一份 WiFi PHY 学习计划\n2. 按照先时域后频域的流程\n3. 每天学习一个小时\n4. 难度适合芯片验证工程师角色\n5. 学习内容写入飞书文档\n6. 发送给用户\n\n这涉及到飞书文档操作，我需要使用 feishu-doc skill。让我先读取这个 skill。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我来帮你规划这份学习计划，并写入飞书文档。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ae4f5bcc152c40a8a47317b0","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\dist\\extensions\\feishu\\skills\\feishu-doc\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":19742,"output":233,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19975,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774746751953,"responseId":"26b9c307fca0c1a83ae91ee4d24ae955"}}
{"type":"message","id":"976af19a","parentId":"0ef5904d","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:12:41.376Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ae4f5bcc152c40a8a47317b0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-doc\ndescription: |\n  Feishu document read/write operations. Activate when user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or docx links.\n---\n\n# Feishu Document Tool\n\nSingle tool `feishu_doc` with action parameter for all document operations, including table creation for Docx.\n\n## Token Extraction\n\nFrom URL `https://xxx.feishu.cn/docx/ABC123def` → `doc_token` = `ABC123def`\n\n## Actions\n\n### Read Document\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"read\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\" }\n```\n\nReturns: title, plain text content, block statistics. Check `hint` field - if present, structured content (tables, images) exists that requires `list_blocks`.\n\n### Write Document (Replace All)\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"write\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"# Title\\n\\nMarkdown content...\" }\n```\n\nReplaces entire document with markdown content. Supports: headings, lists, code blocks, quotes, links, images (`![](url)` auto-uploaded), bold/italic/strikethrough.\n\n**Limitation:** Markdown tables are NOT supported.\n\n### Append Content\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"append\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"content\": \"Additional content\" }\n```\n\nAppends markdown to end of document.\n\n### Create Document\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"create\", \"title\": \"New Document\", \"owner_open_id\": \"ou_xxx\" }\n```\n\nWith folder:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create\",\n  \"title\": \"New Document\",\n  \"folder_token\": \"fldcnXXX\",\n  \"owner_open_id\": \"ou_xxx\"\n}\n```\n\n**Important:** Always pass `owner_open_id` with the requesting user's `open_id` (from inbound metadata `sender_id`) so the user automatically gets `full_access` permission on the created document. Without this, only the bot app has access.\n\n### List Blocks\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"list_blocks\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\" }\n```\n\nReturns full block data including tables, images. Use this to read structured content.\n\n### Get Single Block\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"get_block\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\" }\n```\n\n### Update Block Text\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"update_block\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\",\n  \"content\": \"New text\"\n}\n```\n\n### Delete Block\n\n```json\n{ \"action\": \"delete_block\", \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\", \"block_id\": \"doxcnXXX\" }\n```\n\n### Create Table (Docx Table Block)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create_table\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"row_size\": 2,\n  \"column_size\": 2,\n  \"column_width\": [200, 200]\n}\n```\n\nOptional: `parent_block_id` to insert under a specific block.\n\n### Write Table Cells\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"write_table_cells\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"table_block_id\": \"doxcnTABLE\",\n  \"values\": [\n    [\"A1\", \"B1\"],\n    [\"A2\", \"B2\"]\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### Create Table With Values (One-step)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create_table_with_values\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"row_size\": 2,\n  \"column_size\": 2,\n  \"column_width\": [200, 200],\n  \"values\": [\n    [\"A1\", \"B1\"],\n    [\"A2\", \"B2\"]\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nOptional: `parent_block_id` to insert under a specific block.\n\n### Upload Image to Docx (from URL or local file)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_image\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"url\": \"https://example.com/image.png\"\n}\n```\n\nOr local path with position control:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_image\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"file_path\": \"/tmp/image.png\",\n  \"parent_block_id\": \"doxcnParent\",\n  \"index\": 5\n}\n```\n\nOptional `index` (0-based) inserts the image at a specific position among sibling blocks. Omit to append at end.\n\n**Note:** Image display size is determined by the uploaded image's pixel dimensions. For small images (e.g. 480x270 GIFs), scale to 800px+ width before uploading to ensure proper display.\n\n### Upload File Attachment to Docx (from URL or local file)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_file\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"url\": \"https://example.com/report.pdf\"\n}\n```\n\nOr local path:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"upload_file\",\n  \"doc_token\": \"ABC123def\",\n  \"file_path\": \"/tmp/report.pdf\",\n  \"filename\": \"Q1-report.pdf\"\n}\n```\n\nRules:\n\n- exactly one of `url` / `file_path`\n- optional `filename` override\n- optional `parent_block_id`\n\n## Reading Workflow\n\n1. Start with `action: \"read\"` - get plain text + statistics\n2. Check `block_types` in response for Table, Image, Code, etc.\n3. If structured content exists, use `action: \"list_blocks\"` for full data\n\n## Configuration\n\n```yaml\nchannels:\n  feishu:\n    tools:\n      doc: true # default: true\n```\n\n**Note:** `feishu_wiki` depends on this tool - wiki page content is read/written via `feishu_doc`.\n\n## Permissions\n\nRequired: `docx:document`, `docx:document:readonly`, `docx:document.block:convert`, `drive:drive`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774746761376}}
{"type":"message","id":"cf2ffa3e","parentId":"976af19a","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:12:51.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要：\n1. 先创建一份学习计划的内容\n2. 创建飞书文档\n3. 写入内容\n4. 发送给用户\n\n用户是芯片验证工程师，需要适合他角色的难度。学习计划应该：\n- 先时域后频域\n- 每天一小时\n- 适合验证工程师的实践视角\n\n让我先创建文档，然后写入内容。用户的 open_id 是 `ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf`。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我来创建飞书文档并写入学习计划："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7ec37cfd573640f798438650","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"claw feishu doc create --title \"WiFi PHY 学习计划（时域→频域）\" --owner_open_id \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":21186,"output":298,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21484,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774746761377,"responseId":"0f9e56cd53865dc3e45a8dc06b947ca4"}}
