{"type":"message","id":"f90f98c0","parentId":"55614a9b","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:16:05.583Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Feishu 插件已经加载了，并且注册了 `feishu_doc` 工具。但这个工具可能没有直接暴露给我。让我尝试通过 Gateway 调用这个工具...\n\n实际上，根据 OpenClaw 的架构，工具应该通过 Gateway 暴露给 agent。让我尝试使用 openclaw agent 命令或者查看是否有其他方式调用这些工具。\n\n或者，我可以尝试直接使用 feishu API 通过 HTTP 请求创建文档。但这需要访问令牌。\n\n让我尝试另一种方法：使用 openclaw message 命令发送消息，同时准备学习计划内容。如果无法创建文档，我可以将内容直接发送给用户。\n\n实际上，让我重新审视这个问题。根据工具列表，我有 message 工具，但没有 feishu_doc 工具。这可能是因为 feishu_doc 是一个扩展工具，而不是核心工具。\n\n让我尝试查看 openclaw 是否有其他方式调用这些工具...\n\n或者，我可以直接通过 HTTP API 调用飞书文档 API。但这需要知道 API endpoint 和认证信息。\n\n让我尝试另一个方法：查看 feishu 插件的配置，看看是否有 API endpoint 可用...\n\n实际上，我认为最简单的方法是：\n1. 准备学习计划内容\n2. 直接发送给用户（通过飞书消息）\n3. 同时创建一个本地文件，用户可以自己复制到飞书文档\n\n\n4. 先尝试通过 message 工具发送消息，同时探索是否能访问 feishu API。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Feishu 插件已加载。让我通过 Gateway 调用飞书文档 API 来创建文档："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_547a97de2bac4b92a7d66ac7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw agent --help"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":29332,"output":655,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29987,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774746951017,"responseId":"4c5afc4b5ccb2b7f89b7cc260ebe8914"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f0f22c9","parentId":"f90f98c0","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:16:07.189Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_547a97de2bac4b92a7d66ac7","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.24 (cff6dc9) — Automation with claws: minimal fuss, maximal pinch.\n\nUsage: openclaw agent [options]\n\nRun an agent turn via the Gateway (use --local for embedded)\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>               Agent id (overrides routing bindings)\n  --channel <channel>        Delivery channel:\n                             last|telegram|whatsapp|discord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|line\n                             (omit to use the main session channel)\n  --deliver                  Send the agent's reply back to the selected channel\n                             (default: false)\n  -h, --help                 Display help for command\n  --json                     Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  --local                    Run the embedded agent locally (requires model\n                             provider API keys in your shell) (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>       Message body for the agent\n  --reply-account <id>       Delivery account id override\n  --reply-channel <channel>  Delivery channel override (separate from routing)\n  --reply-to <target>        Delivery target override (separate from session\n                             routing)\n  --session-id <id>          Use an explicit session id\n  -t, --to <number>          Recipient number in E.164 used to derive the\n                             session key\n  --thinking <level>         Thinking level: off | minimal | low | medium | high\n                             | xhigh\n  --timeout <seconds>        Override agent command timeout (seconds, default\n                             600 or config value)\n  --verbose <on|off>         Persist agent verbose level for the session\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"status update\"\n    Start a new session.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Summarize logs\"\n    Use a specific agent.\n  openclaw agent --session-id 1234 --message \"Summarize inbox\" --thinking medium\n    Target a session with explicit thinking level.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Trace logs\" --verbose on --json\n    Enable verbose logging and JSON output.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Summon reply\" --deliver\n    Deliver reply.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Generate report\" --deliver --reply-channel slack --reply-to \"#reports\"\n    Send reply to a different channel/target.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agent"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1601,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.24 (cff6dc9) — Automation with claws: minimal fuss, maximal pinch.\n\nUsage: openclaw agent [options]\n\nRun an agent turn via the Gateway (use --local for embedded)\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>               Agent id (overrides routing bindings)\n  --channel <channel>        Delivery channel:\n                             last|telegram|whatsapp|discord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|line\n                             (omit to use the main session channel)\n  --deliver                  Send the agent's reply back to the selected channel\n                             (default: false)\n  -h, --help                 Display help for command\n  --json                     Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  --local                    Run the embedded agent locally (requires model\n                             provider API keys in your shell) (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>       Message body for the agent\n  --reply-account <id>       Delivery account id override\n  --reply-channel <channel>  Delivery channel override (separate from routing)\n  --reply-to <target>        Delivery target override (separate from session\n                             routing)\n  --session-id <id>          Use an explicit session id\n  -t, --to <number>          Recipient number in E.164 used to derive the\n                             session key\n  --thinking <level>         Thinking level: off | minimal | low | medium | high\n                             | xhigh\n  --timeout <seconds>        Override agent command timeout (seconds, default\n                             600 or config value)\n  --verbose <on|off>         Persist agent verbose level for the session\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"status update\"\n    Start a new session.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Summarize logs\"\n    Use a specific agent.\n  openclaw agent --session-id 1234 --message \"Summarize inbox\" --thinking medium\n    Target a session with explicit thinking level.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Trace logs\" --verbose on --json\n    Enable verbose logging and JSON output.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Summon reply\" --deliver\n    Deliver reply.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Generate report\" --deliver --reply-channel slack --reply-to \"#reports\"\n    Send reply to a different channel/target.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agent","cwd":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774746967188}}
{"type":"message","id":"64a02909","parentId":"9f0f22c9","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:16:13.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我尝试直接通过 Gateway 发送请求来创建飞书文档。我需要找到正确的方式来调用 feishu_doc 工具。\n\n实际上，让我检查 Gateway 的状态和配置，看看是否有 API endpoint 可以直接调用：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我先检查 Gateway 状态，然后直接通过 HTTP 调用飞书文档 API："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b681e2048ab64c1bbf34b101","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway status"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":30232,"output":127,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30359,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774746967192,"responseId":"157ad9b283af4b89fca88ddfaf45658d"}}
