{"type":"message","id":"073371f9","parentId":"99144b71","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:23:12.066Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，文件已保存。现在让我使用飞书 API 创建文档。我需要获取 tenant_access_token，然后调用飞书文档 API。\n\n让我写一个脚本来完成这个任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在让我通过飞书 API 创建文档："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9d3a530e229c4000957b76c0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$appId = \"cli_a9340a6fd922dcc6\"\n$appSecret = \"iEXatjRUBk8cCfedbOBlibZ6ZkYCJeN0\"\n\n# 获取 tenant_access_token\n$tokenResponse = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" -Method Post -ContentType \"application/json\" -Body (@{app_id=$appId; app_secret=$appSecret} | ConvertTo-Json)\n$token = $tokenResponse.tenant_access_token\n\nWrite-Host \"Token obtained: $($token.Substring(0,20))...\"\n\n# 创建文档\n$createBody = @{\n    document = @{\n        title = \"WiFi PHY 学习计划（时域→频域）\"\n    }\n} | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 3\n\n$headers = @{\n    \"Authorization\" = \"Bearer $token\"\n    \"Content-Type\" = \"application/json\"\n}\n\n$docResponse = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents\" -Method Post -Headers $headers -Body $createBody\n$docToken = $docResponse.data.document.document_id\n\nWrite-Host \"Document created: $docToken\"\nWrite-Host \"Document URL: https://feishu.cn/docx/$docToken\"\n\n# 输出 docToken 供后续使用\n$docToken"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":53558,"output":395,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53953,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774747379964,"responseId":"538c97852da4256cc58e7c593f907b07"}}
