{"type":"message","id":"637d9bd8","parentId":"b1f420b4","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:30:13.658Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文档创建成功了，但是 root block ID 为空。这可能是因为飞书 API 的返回格式问题。让我查看一下完整的文档信息。\n\n实际上，文档已经创建成功了，URL 是 https://feishu.cn/docx/JZt7diQjuoWP1kxsay7coU7fnub\n\n让我尝试另一种方法来写入内容，或者直接把链接发给用户，让用户自己查看。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6d34b736047c49b486f95460","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$temp = Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot\\feishu_temp.json\" | ConvertFrom-Json\n$token = $temp.token\n$docToken = $temp.docToken\n\n$headers = @{\n    \"Authorization\" = \"Bearer $token\"\n    \"Content-Type\" = \"application/json\"\n}\n\n# 获取文档信息\n$docInfo = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/$docToken\" -Method Get -Headers $headers\n\nWrite-Host \"Document info:\"\n$docInfo | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":70866,"output":316,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71182,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774747800776,"responseId":"9bb24f71b0bf98041ff8bceee87a66e7"}}
