{"type":"message","id":"ba8cd1f7","parentId":"1c61391f","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:42:25.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"读取成功，说明权限是对的。现在让我尝试写入内容。问题是 batch_create API 返回 404。让我尝试其他方法：\n\n1. 使用 update_block 来更新页面内容\n2. 或者使用 children API 来添加子块\n\n让我尝试使用 update_block。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_286e316623db4e16a13d4510","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$token = (Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot\\feishu_temp.json\" | ConvertFrom-Json).token\n$docToken = \"JZt7diQjuoWP1kxsay7coU7fnub\"\n\n$headers = @{\n    \"Authorization\" = \"Bearer $token\"\n    \"Content-Type\" = \"application/json\"\n}\n\n# 尝试更新 page block 的内容\n$body = @{\n    update_text_elements = @{\n        elements = @(\n            @{\n                text_run = @{\n                    content = \"WiFi PHY 学习计划（时域→频域）\"\n                }\n            }\n        )\n    }\n} | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5\n\n$url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/$docToken/blocks/$docToken\"\n\ntry {\n    $response = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $url -Method Patch -Headers $headers -Body $body\n    Write-Host \"Update successful:\"\n    $response | ConvertTo-Json\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"Error: $($_.ErrorDetails.Message)\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":87717,"output":360,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88077,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774748529952,"responseId":"a38ac90900ec707b7a22f2b5fdad4beb"}}
