{"type":"message","id":"e1ccbe3f","parentId":"4e7281a1","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:42:44.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"成功了！现在文档的标题已经更新了。让我继续添加更多内容。我需要使用 children API 来添加子块。让我尝试使用正确的 API。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"成功更新了标题！现在让我添加完整的学习计划内容："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8fa8ab37c697416e97c3f506","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$token = (Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot\\feishu_temp.json\" | ConvertFrom-Json).token\n$docToken = \"JZt7diQjuoWP1kxsay7coU7fnub\"\n\n$headers = @{\n    \"Authorization\" = \"Bearer $token\"\n    \"Content-Type\" = \"application/json\"\n}\n\n# 使用 children 的 POST API 来添加子块\n# 根据飞书 API 文档，正确的路径应该是 /documents/{doc_id}/blocks/{block_id}/children\n$body = @{\n    index = 0\n    children = @(\n        @{\n            block_type = 4\n            paragraph = @{\n                elements = @(@{text_run = @{content = \"专为芯片验证工程师设计 | 每日1小时 | 12周系统学习\"}})\n            }\n        },\n        @{\n            block_type = 15\n            divider = @{}\n        },\n        @{\n            block_type = 2\n            heading2 = @{\n                elements = @(@{text_run = @{content = \"第一阶段：时域基础（4周）\"}})\n            }\n        }\n    )\n} | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 10\n\n$url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/$docToken/blocks/$docToken/children\"\n\nWrite-Host \"Adding content blocks...\"\ntry {\n    $response = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $url -Method Post -Headers $headers -Body $body\n    Write-Host \"Success!\"\n    $response | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 3\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"Error: $($_.ErrorDetails.Message)\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":88182,"output":444,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88626,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774748545951,"responseId":"