{"type":"message","id":"4d297e1f","parentId":"8353a78c","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:51:49.312Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文档的 block_type 是 1 (page)，标题已经写入。现在需要添加子 blocks。让我尝试另一种 API 格式 - 先更新 page block 的文本内容，添加更多文本元素。\n\n或者我需要尝试不同的方法 - 使用 document_id 而不是 block_id 作为父级。让我尝试先在文档末尾追加内容。\n\n根据飞书 API 文档，创建子块的正确方式是 POST /documents/{document_id}/blocks/{block_id}/children。让我再次检查请求格式。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_981a99a81e674ef49c5cd913","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$appId = \"cli_a9340a6fd922dcc6\"\n$appSecret = \"iEXatjRUBk8cCfedbOBlibZ6ZkYCJeN0\"\n$docToken = \"JZt7diQjuoWP1kxsay7coU7fnub\"\n\n# 获取 token\n$tokenResponse = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" -Method Post -ContentType \"application/json\" -Body (@{app_id=$appId; app_secret=$appSecret} | ConvertTo-Json)\n$token = $tokenResponse.tenant_access_token\n\n$headers = @{\n    \"Authorization\" = \"Bearer $token\"\n    \"Content-Type\" = \"application/json\"\n}\n\n# 使用 Patch 更新 page block，在现有文本后追加内容\n$updateBody = @{\n    update_text_elements = @{\n        elements = @(\n            @{\n                text_run = @{\n                    content = \"WiFi PHY 学习计划（时域→频域）\n\n专为芯片验证工程师设计 | 每日1小时 | 12周系统学习\n\n---\n\n第一阶段：时域基础（4周）\n\nWeek 1-2：信号与系统基础\n目标：建立时域分析的数学基础\n• Day 1: 时域信号基础 - 周期信号、能量/功率信号\n• Day 2: 线性系统响应 - 冲激响应、卷积运算\n• Day 3: 相关函数 - 自相关、互相关、匹配滤波\n• Day 4: 噪声模型 - AWGN、信噪比定义\n• Day 5: 带限信号 - 采样定理回顾\n• Day 6-7: 复习+实践\n\nWeek 3-4：WiFi时域信号结构\n• Day 8: PPDU帧结构\n• Day 9: 短训练序列\n• Day 10: 长训练序列\n• Day 11: SIGNAL字段\n• Day 12: 数据符号\n• Day 13-14: 复习+实践\n\n---\n\n第二阶段：同步与定时（3周）\n\nWeek 5-6：时域同步技术\n• Day 15: 包检测\n• Day 16: 符号定时\n• Day 17: 载波频偏估计\n• Day 18: 采样频偏\n• Day 19: 相位噪声\n• Day 20-21: 复习+实践\n\nWeek 7：同步验证方法论\n• Day 22: 同步测试向量\n• Day 23: 时序检查\n• Day 24: 覆盖率分析\n\n---\n\n第三阶段：频域基础（3周）\n\nWeek 8-9：FFT与OFDM原理\n• Day 25: DFT/FFT原理\n• Day 26: OFDM调制\n• Day 27: 循环前缀\n• Day 28: 子载波间隔\n• Day 29: 导频子载波\n• Day 30-31: 复习+实践\n\nWeek 10：信道估计与均衡\n• Day 32: 信道模型\n• Day 33: LS信道估计\n• Day 34: 信道平滑\n• Day 35: 均衡器设计\n\n---\n\n第四阶段：进阶主题（2周）\n\nWeek 11：MIMO与波束成形\n• Day 36: 空间复用\n• Day 37: 信道探测\n• Day 38: 波束成形\n• Day 39: MU-MIMO\n\nWeek 12：WiFi 7新特性\n• Day 40: 320MHz带宽\n• Day 41: 4096-QAM\n• Day 42: Multi-RU\n• Day 43-45: 总复习\n\n---\n\n学习建议\n1. 理论与实践结合\n2. 建立知识图谱\n3. 关注验证视角\n4. 记录问题\n5. 定期回顾\n\n---\n\n推荐资源\n• 802.11-2020 标准\n• 802.11ax/y/z 修正案\n• Wireless Communications - Andrea Goldsmith\n• MATLAB WLAN Toolbox 文档\"\n                }\n            }\n        )\n    }\n} | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 10\n\n$url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/$docToken/blocks/$docToken\"\n\ntry {\n    $response = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $url -Method Patch -Headers $headers -Body $updateBody\n    Write-Host \"Document content updated successfully!\"\n    Write-Host \"Document URL: https://feishu.cn/docx/$docToken\"\n    $response | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 2\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"Error: $($_.ErrorDetails.Message)\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":92375,"output":1255,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93630,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774749068870,"responseId":"0e9d8968c9e3ea56d51cc488d30a414c"}}
