{"type":"message","id":"2a3144c5","parentId":"196e774b","timestamp":"2026-03-29T01:52:17.462Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"成功了！文档内容已经写入完成。让我更新一下 memory 记录。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**✅ 完成！**\n\n**WiFi PHY 学习计划**已成功写入飞书文档！\n\n📚 **文档链接**：https://feishu.cn/docx/JZt7diQjuoWP1kxsay7coU7fnub\n\n**学习计划包含：**\n| 阶段 | 时长 | 内容 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 第一阶段 | 4周 | 时域基础（信号系统 + WiFi帧结构） |\n| 第二阶段 | 3周 | 同步与定时（同步技术 + 验证方法） |\n| 第三阶段 | 3周 | 频域基础（FFT/OFDM + 信道均衡） |\n| 第四阶段 | 2周 | 进阶主题（MIMO + WiFi 7） |\n\n🎯 **每天1小时，12周系统学习！**\n\n有问题随时问我～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":94688,"output":213,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94901,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774749125735,"responseId":"0c9c873ba1e8f49a4b07a942ce68f011"}}
