{"type":"message","id":"d81e99ab","parentId":"f9b45a18","timestamp":"2026-03-29T16:38:15.999Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户有很多专业文档，包括：\n\n1. **协议&标准**：\n   - 802.11-be.pdf\n   - 802.11ax.pdf\n   - WIFI7的PHY.pdf\n   - AMBA-AXI3协议\n   - IEEE 1800-2023 SV标准\n   - IEEE 18002-2020-UVM\n   - UVM用户指南\n\n2. **设计书籍**：\n   - Verilog HDL相关书籍\n   - testbench编写\n   - 数字电路设计\n\n3. **验证书籍**：\n   - SystemVerilog验证\n   - UVM实战\n   - 验证方法论\n\n这些文档很多都是PDF，我需要读取它们。但是PDF文件可能很大，我需要先尝试读取一些关键的文档。\n\n让我首先读取WiFi相关的标准文档和验证相关的核心书籍。由于这些是PDF，我可能需要使用read工具来读取它们。\n\n让我先尝试读取WiFi 7 PHY相关的文档，这对用户的WiFi验证工作最相关。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"发现了丰富的专业资料库！让我分类学习："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_409b3bc1542e442b837d988c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$files = @(\n    \"D:\\飞书\\协议&标准\\802.11-be.pdf\",\n    \"D:\\飞书\\协议&标准\\802.11ax.pdf\", \n    \"D:\\飞书\\协议&标准\\WIFI7的PHY.pdf\",\n    \"D:\\飞书\\验证书籍\\System Verilog验证系统入门\",\n    \"D:\\飞书\\验证书籍\\UVM实战(完整版).pdf\"\n)\n\nWrite-Host \"=== 发现的专业资料 ===\" -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# 统计文件\n$categories = @{\n    \"WiFi/协议标准\" = (Get-ChildItem \"D:\\飞书\\协议&标准\" -File).Count\n    \"设计书籍\" = (Get-ChildItem \"D:\\飞书\\设计书籍\" -File).Count\n    \"验证书籍\" = (Get-ChildItem \"D:\\飞书\\验证书籍\" -File -Recurse).Count\n}\n\nforeach ($cat in $categories.GetEnumerator()) {\n    Write-Host \"📚 $($cat.Key): $($cat.Value) 个文件\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"总计: $(($categories.Values | Measure-Object -Sum).Sum) 个专业文档\" -ForegroundColor Yellow"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":58660,"output":712,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59372,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774802269435,"responseId":"f643bde9dcba98b3ea28e2e0fe23d9fc"}}
